UID:10001182-1774206000-1774206000@northshorecenter.org
SUMMARY:Solstice: A Winter Circus Experience
DESCRIPTION:Step into a dreamscape with “Solstice: a Winter Circus Experience” by Circus EVO. At the heart of the story is a girl who loses her light and stumbles into a world where time bends\, memories breathe\, and the familiar becomes impossibly strange. Shadows dance\, snow drifts fall\, and acrobats blur the line between the everyday and the extraordinary. More than a circus\, “Solstice” is a living poem — a place where nostalgia meets surreal wonder\, and where audiences are invited to rediscover the childlike awe of seeing snow for the first time! \nIn 2026\, Solstice returns with all-new elements and an original score composed by NC artist Bella Nona\, weaving music\, movement\, and imagination into a one-of-a-kind celebration of the human spirit. Don’t Miss it! \n \nAbout Circus EVO:\nCircus EVO is an International Circus Company based in North Carolina. Since 2020 we’ve transformed urban spaces into vibrant stages\, bridging the gap between art and community through Contemporary Circus\, Dance\, Music\, Theater\, and more! Our Mission to EVOke Emotions and EVOlve Circus Art empowers Artists of all backgrounds\, while bringing a new way to entertain and provide cultural value to our community. \nOver the past 5 years\, we have emerged as a dynamic force\, dedicated to delivering high-quality\, multi-disciplinary performances. Since our inception\, Circus EVO has performed over 70 times in 11 cities for thousands of people\, supporting more than 70 artists and creatives along the way.
URL:https://northshorecenter.org/event/solstice/
LOCATION:George Van Dusen Theatre
CATEGORIES:Theatre
END:VEVENT
